<%= provide(:body_id, 'index') %>
<%= provide(:result, '报表查看') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>时刻点所对应的得分排名表</h1>

        <p>
          本排名表提取指定时刻的评分数据而生成，各项评分均根据其所对应的评分规则进行处理，如对结果有异议，可申请核对。
        </p>
        <br/>

        <p class="hidden-phone">
          <a class="btn btn-info btn-large pull-right">详细指南请猛击此处 &raquo;...</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li>
          <a href="/">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-home"></i>
            首页
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
          <a href="/reports">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
            测试评分报表
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
          <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
          选择日周月报表
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
        <div class="span12">
          <h4 class="title">出口得分排名表如下示：</h4>

          <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
          <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-radmin">
            <thead>
            <tr>
              <th style="text-align:center;">源结节名称</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">目的节点名称</th>
              <% @title_name.each do |tn| %>
                <th style="text-align:center;"><%= tn %></th>
              <% end %>
              <th style="text-align:center;">总正分</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">总负分</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">总分</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <% @odata.each do |line| %>
              <tr>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[0] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[1] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[2] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[3] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[4] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[5] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[6] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[7] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[8] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><span class="label label-info"><%= line[9] %></span></td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p></p>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="well center">
        <div class="pagination pagination-small center offset4">
          <%= will_paginate @odata, :inner_window => 2 %>
        </div>
        <div class="offset4">
          统计信息：一共有 <%= @odata.total_entries %>  条,当前第 <%= @odata.current_page %> 页, 共
          <% if (@odata.total_entries % @odata.per_page) ==0 %>
            <%= (@odata.total_entries / @odata.per_page) %> 页.
          <% else %>
            <%= (@odata.total_entries / @odata.per_page) +1 %> 页
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          Etiam varius erat in nisl egestas id auctor lacus consectetur.
          Ut dui risus, auctor a malesuada volutpat, tempus sit amet arcu.
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">Jane Doe via Mobile</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
